verses.text_plain: O Lord our Lord, how excellent is thy name in all the earth! who hast set thy glory above the heavens.
verses.verse_html: 1O Lord our Lord, how excellent is thy name in all the earth! who hast set thy glory above the heavens.

verses.text_plain: Out of the mouth of babes and sucklings hast thou ordained strength because of thine enemies, that thou mightest still the enemy and the avenger.
verses.verse_html:
2Out of the mouth of babes and sucklings hast thou ordained strength because of thine enemies, that thou mightest still the enemy and the avenger. ▼
▼ ordained: Heb. founded

verses.text_plain: When I consider thy heavens, the work of thy fingers, the moon and the stars, which thou hast ordained;
verses.verse_html: 3When I consider thy heavens, the work of thy fingers, the moon and the stars, which thou hast ordained;

verses.text_plain: What is man, that thou art mindful of him? and the son of man, that thou visitest him?
verses.verse_html: 4What is man, that thou art mindful of him? and the son of man, that thou visitest him?

verses.text_plain: For thou hast made him a little lower than the angels, and hast crowned him with glory and honour.
verses.verse_html: 5For thou hast made him a little lower than the angels, and hast crowned him with glory and honour.

tokens.text: For thou hast made him a little

verses.text_plain: Thou madest him to have dominion over the works of thy hands; thou hast put all things under his feet:
verses.verse_html: 6Thou madest him to have dominion over the works of thy hands; thou hast put all things under his feet:

tokens.text: Thou madest him to have dominion

verses.text_plain: All sheep and oxen, yea, and the beasts of the field;
verses.verse_html:
7All sheep and oxen, yea, and the beasts of the field; ▼
▼ All…: Heb. Flocks and oxen all of them

footnotes.body_text: ▼ All…: Heb. Flocks and oxen all of them
footnotes.body_html: ▼ All…: Heb. Flocks and oxen all of them

verses.text_plain: The fowl of the air, and the fish of the sea, and whatsoever passeth through the paths of the seas.
verses.verse_html: 8The fowl of the air, and the fish of the sea, and whatsoever passeth through the paths of the seas.

verses.text_plain: O Lord our Lord, how excellent is thy name in all the earth!
verses.verse_html: 9O Lord our Lord, how excellent is thy name in all the earth!
